Patricia Dunn (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricia_Dunn_(actress) 0 Partricia Dunn (1930 – May 3, 1990) was an American actress. She was a dancer in many Broadway plays. She died of lung cancer in 1990. Partricia_Dunn ( 1930 – May_3_,_1990 ) was an_American_actress . She was a_dancer in many_Broadway_plays . She died of lung_cancer in 1990 .
